Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other choice. The burden is too great for her to bear alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.89,0:01:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably at her limit already.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.61,0:01:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can't! Not alone, at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.55,0:01:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment you give up, it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, you can change your fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.18,0:02:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.29,0:02:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to change the course of this destruction and grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the power you were blessed with was meant for this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.71,0:02:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can someone like me really do that much?{change the outcome}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.76,0:02:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I really change this outcome?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.91,0:02:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you should make a contract with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and become a Magical Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a dream?
