Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:25.36,EPISODE TITLE,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an0\fad(236,0)\pos(311,319)}Episode 1   As if I met her in a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuya went to get her. You should give him a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.97,0:04:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, it's morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up! Mama, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama's finally up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.47,0:05:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it been going lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitomi got another love letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes three this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. Guys who don't even have the courage to confess aren't worth your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's Kazuko doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still using homeroom to talk about her boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This week is her three month anniversary. It's a new record.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd have thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.19,0:05:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a really crucial time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:06:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's not for real, this is around the time problems start to arise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she can make it past this, she should be fine for another year or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.34,0:06:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which ribbon should I pick?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Isn't it a little flashy?{TLC Note:  "tacky"?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be all over if a woman was judged only by her looks.{What world does she live in?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.23,0:06:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it great? This way Madoka's secret admirers will all be mesmerised.{"hypnotized"? "captivated"?  It really means: "madly in love"  "Mesmerised" is fine, though.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to pretend that you have some. It's the secret of beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:06:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Make sure you eat it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like another cup of coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.43,0:07:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a safe trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka, you should hurry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.71,0:07:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a safe trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a safe trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka, you're so slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! That's a really cute ribbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:07:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? It's not too flashy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks very nice on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.97,0:08:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. And then she said that guys who use love letters instead of confessing in-person aren't worth the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka's mom is always so cool, and she's beautiful and career-minded to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we could be like that, we wouldn't have anything to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like someone's jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How nice... I wouldn't mind receiving one myself. A love letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Does Madoka want to become a popular beauty like Hitomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you perhaps trying to change your image with that ribbon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that! This was Mama's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've learned the secret to becoming popular from your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inexcusable! You little rascal! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.48,0:08:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you a cute one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.06,0:08:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I definitely won't forgive you for trying to get popular with the guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka is to become my bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I have something very important to announce.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is better? Eggs hard-boiled, or soft-boiled?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakazawa, please answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... It's fine either way, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.41,0:09:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eggzactly! Either way is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging a woman's charm by the way she prepares eggs is a grave error! {TLC Note:  "charisma"?  "Charm" desu ne?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To all you girls, be careful never to date guys who only eat soft-boiled eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.99,0:09:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like things didn't work out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as for you guys, make sure you don't become the sort of person who nitpicks about things like eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moving right along...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to introduce a new transfer student!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She tells us that last?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:10:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akemi-san, please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! She's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah, she's a beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's have you introduce yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Akemi Homura. It's nice to meet you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Akemi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What school did you come from, Akemi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.74,0:11:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I attended a missionary school in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you in any clubs?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sports? Arts?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never joined any.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have such nice hair. What brand of shampoo do you use?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Akemi-san sure has a mysterious air about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Madoka. Do you know her from somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed like she was looking right at you just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry. I think all the excitement has gotten to me. I feel faint.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me, but I would like to go to the nurse's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me show you where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I don't want to cause you any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask the person on duty.{TLC Note: "kakari no hito", "person in charge/duty person"}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname Madoka, you're the nurse's representative for this class, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you accompany me to the nurse's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know I'm the health representative?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.19,0:12:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saotome-sensei told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.51,0:12:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Well, the nurse's room is just—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's this way, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.29,0:12:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... Is it possible that you already know where it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.58,0:12:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... Akemi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.14,0:12:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homura is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homura-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.48,0:12:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's a pretty unique name, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean... I didn't mean it was weird or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it sounds kind of cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname Madoka, do you truly value your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you value your friends and family?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... O-Of course I do. They all mean a lot to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love all of them. They're all very important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.92,0:13:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.84,0:13:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. If that is really true...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then you have no reason to become someone other than who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, you might lose everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just continue living the life of Kaname Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as it always has been.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she just break the school record?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.73,0:15:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she was perfect, good in sports and academics. But it turns out she's really nuts. {TL: really radio wave wtf? TLC: Lol, reminds me of Fruits Basket with that. Saying she is nuts or nonsensical will work, but I have sometimes seen it taken litterly, like in FB, as  electric/radio wave girl.}{Just an FYI: this is the guy translating the show.Christ.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.35,0:15:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many things must she excel in before she's satisfied?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Moe"? Is what they call "moe"?!{tlc: sounds like "moika, soko ga moe nano ka" to me, so I would say either go with jealousy since it fits or infatuation/a crush if you think it was moe, although moe doesnt seem to fit here.}{Who's this retarded TLC?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.84,0:15:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka-san, is this really the first time you've met Akemi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.80,0:15:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under normal circumstances, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean? Did you meet her under some strange circumstances before?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.42,0:15:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I saw her in a dream last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fresh! Madoka's showing some character!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You meanie! I was really worried about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be something from a past life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.97,0:15:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are destined companions who have traversed time and space to meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of dream was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just know that it was really weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:16:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be that you really have met Akemi-san before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though you don't remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.97,0:16:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...perhaps her image was preserved in your sub-conscious, and that was reflected in your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a little far-fetched? It might just be a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.69,0:16:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.78,0:16:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it piano today, or Japanese dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's tea ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But exams are creeping up, so I don't know how long I can keep doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it must be nice being part of a middle-class family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka, is it all right if we go by the CD store on our way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Kamijou-kun again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.03,0:16:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, Madoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:46.96,(17:45) The inside of this store....,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\pos(187,182)}The interior of this store is currently undergoing renovations.\N\N\N\N\N\N\N{\bord0.3}This floor will be closed for the duration.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.78,0:18:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homura-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.19,0:18:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.81,0:18:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. How can you be so cruel?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.43,0:18:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he called for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.74,0:18:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard his cries for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now of all times...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with her? Is she some kind of cosplaying freak?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.01,0:19:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a stuffed animal, right? Is it an animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. But I still have to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.83,0:20:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? Where's the emergency exit? Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so strange. The way keeps changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a joke, right? I must be dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Madoka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:20:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.14,0:21:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a close call.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you were able to save Kyubei?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. He is my dear friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He called for me. I could hear his voice inside my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.44,0:21:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.67,0:21:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That uniform... You're from Mitagihara, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.54,0:21:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second years?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I should introduce myself first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.51,0:21:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.23,0:21:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind if I finished up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.59,0:22:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.33,0:22:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It changed back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.16,0:22:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Witch fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.94,0:22:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to catch it, you'd better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.57,0:22:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you go this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something else I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.30,0:22:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not very bright, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.38,0:22:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying I'll let you leave unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.59,0:23:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not looking for unnecessary trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.16,0:23:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Mami. You saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.95,0:23:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be thanking these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.05,0:23:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to pass by.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.91,0:23:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much! My name is Kyubei.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.52,0:23:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you the one who was calling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.88,0:23:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Kaname Madoka and Miki Sayaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.67,0:23:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know our names?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.35,0:23:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a request for both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.59,0:23:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A request?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.70,0:24:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to make a contract with me and become a Magical Girl!
