Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.99,0:24:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the power to grant any wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.77,0:24:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.85,0:24:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.06,0:24:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything will do. I will grant any miracle, no matter what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.45,0:24:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me really happy.
